snippet.title: Monster Hunter Generations - Deviant Monsters Game Trailer - Nintendo E3 2016
snippet.description:
Check out the official game trailer for Monster Hunter Generations from Nintendo E3 2016. 

Powerful enemies like the Grimclaw Tigrex have survived previous hunter encounters and have taken on new traits and abilities. These are sure to provide a challenge for even the most seasoned hunters.

Check out more information here! http://e3.nintendo.com/games/monster-hunter-generations-3ds
